<plot>GUN is the story of a gun. A gun that has the power to move from place to place on its own volition. The Gun gives a street punk the power to climb the ladder of criminality from shoplifter to killer; then it leads a frightened fisherman down the trail of thoughtless action. With each incident, the gun grows stronger in power, until ultimately, in the final scene, it pulls its' own trigger.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?224801</url></doc>
